Admin --> UC05
Admin --> UC06
Admin --> UC07
Admin --> UC08
Admin --> UC09
Admin --> UC10
Admin --> UC11
Admin --> UC12
Admin --> UC13
Admin --> UC14
Admin --> UC15
Admin --> UC16
Admin --> UC17
Admin --> UC18
Admin --> UC19
Admin --> UC20
Admin --> UC21
Admin --> UC22
Admin --> UC23
Admin --> UC24
Admin --> UC25
Admin --> UC26
Admin --> UC27

Oper --> UC01
Oper --> UC03
Oper --> UC10
Oper --> UC11
Oper --> UC12
Oper --> UC13
Oper --> UC14
Oper --> UC15
Oper --> UC16
Oper --> UC17
Oper --> UC18
Oper --> UC19
Oper --> UC20
Oper --> UC21
Oper --> UC22
Oper --> UC23
Oper --> UC24
Oper --> UC25
Oper --> UC26
Oper --> UC27

Guest --> UC01
Guest --> UC02

' ── Includes / Extends ──
UC12 <. UC10 <<include>>
UC12 <. UC11 <<include>>
UC10 ..> UC14 <<include>>
UC11 ..> UC14 <<include>>
UC10 ..> UC15 <<include>>
UC11 ..> UC15 <<include>>
UC21 ..> UC16 <<include>>
UC21 ..> UC20 <<include>>
